sectionText: All lab sections meet during the first week of classes. Students who miss their first lab session will be immediately dropped and the slot opened for another student. Anyone who adds the class during the first week, and has a lab section that has already met, must immediately contact the lab engineer Dane Sievers (dsievers@illinois.edu). No one may add the class after the first week of the semester.  This lab is held in 259 MNTL.
